CSTutor.Model.Chat

Class ChatWindow

  • java.lang.Object
    • CSTutor.Model.Chat.ChatWindow

  • public class ChatWindow
extends java.lang.Object
    The ChatWindow object is derived from an overall view of Sections 2.6.1 - 2.6.4 of the requirements. The ChatWindow is one of the primary data object of the Chat Tool. The data components of the ChatWindow are a Console window for output and a text box for input.
    Author:
    Stephen Daily
